INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `article_category_id`, `header_en`, `content_en`, `header_th`, `content_th`, `sort_order`, `interest`) VALUES ('27', '2', 'CHETAWAN RETREAT RESORT', '<h2> Office Syndrome Management Program </h2> \r\n<p> 3 days 2 nights/ 5 days 4 nights.\r\n<p> Office Syndrome is an illness that effects to office people nowadays. Some of the symptom includes pain in several parts of the body such as neck, shoulder, arm, wrist, eye socket, back and some other muscles when you are overworked. Those symptoms will occur when you have a constantly work, sitting in the same position with poor posture in front of the monitor over a long period of time. It could be even worse if people ignore the signs and symptoms and do not try to take care of themselves, this could affect the way you work as well. \r\n<p> The Thai Traditional Massage is very effective to help relieve the symptoms of Office Syndrome and it canhelp you get back to working without limitation.\r\n<h3>Included:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li> Wellness Check-up\r\n<li> Thai massage with herbs for treatment service.\r\n<li> Herbal steaming.\r\n<li> Oil massage and Aromatherapy.\r\n<li> Head massage.\r\n<li> Activities for health such as Rue-Si Dutton, Thai boxing, Thai dancing by a specialist.\r\n<li> Spa cuisine. \r\n<li> Three healthy meals a day.\r\n<li> Healthy snacks and beverages.\r\n<li> Daily fitness, pooland leisure activities.\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h2> Lower Back Pain Management Program </h2>\r\n<p> 3 days 2 nights / 5 days 4 nights.\r\n<p> It is certain that people who works in front of the computer all day long, or by sitting, standing, or walking can have lower back pain because the muscles which support the backbone work more and cause them to be tired and tense all day.\r\n<p> Therefore, inappropriate routines can cause peoples lower back to be more painful if they keep doing their routines in that way.   It becomes hard to heal and it can become a chronic pain if they do not change their behavior.\r\n<p> Thai Medical Rehabilitation Program is a very effective program to help cure and rehabilitate lower back pain with other medicines. Also massage for treatment can relieve pain caused from tense muscles and reduce constrictive nerves. Besides, hot herbal compression is an effective remedy for relieving muscle pain and stimulating blood circulation. \r\n<h3>Included:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li> Wellness Check-up.\r\n<li> Thai massage with herbs for treatment service.\r\n<li> Herbal steaming.\r\n<li> Oil massage and Aromatherapy.\r\n<li> Foot massage.\r\n<li> Activities for health such as Rue-Si Dutton, Thai boxing, Thai dancing by a specialist.\r\n<li> Meditation and recreational activities for improving concentration and health such as crafts.\r\n<li> Spa cuisine.\r\n<li> 3 healthy meals a day.\r\n<li> Healthy snacks and beverages.\r\n<li> Daily fitness, pooland leisure activities.\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h2>Mother Health Care Program </h2>\r\n<p> 3 days 2 nights/ 5 days 4 nights/ 7 days 6 nights.\r\n<p> Rehabilitation for women after deliverance is needed because they had to work hard with both body and mind. Furthermore, they had to suffer with the stress and pains during the 9 months of pregnancy.  After that, most of them suddenly became very sad and depress because of hormonal changes. \r\n<p> Rehabilitation as in Thai Traditional Medicine is one alternative medicine to improve mothers health and wellness recently. Then, Thai Traditional Medicine can rehabilitate and relieve the effects to the mother after deliverance, such as, being exhausted, having pains and aches, and releasing amniotic fluid. \r\n<p> During 3 days, 5 days, and 7 days of this program, you will have a good care and treatment from the professional physiotherapist of Thai massage and medical professional. Be trained to eat good and healthy food. \r\n<h3>Included:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li> Wellness Check-up.\r\n<li> Massage for releasing amniotic fluid (waste water).\r\n<li> Herbal steaming.\r\n<li> Sittin